						               													<description>GRAXX is home to a wasteland unlike any you have encountered before, from the mutants roaming the highways to the survivors trying with all their might to cling on to any sense of hope, it is here where damnation reigns supreme.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Toxic Holocaust is a tabletop miniatures game of brutally quick and easy skirmish battles between rival gangs on a post-apocalyptic world, where survival is nothing but a dream, as the reality of living, dying and thrashing is the only truth and one that will kick you in the teeth very, very quickly. Are you ready?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Revisit the original 2009 first edition of Toxic Holocaust, fully restored and remastered. The rules allow you to create gangs and the members of your gangs entirely from scratch, including weapons, traits, abilities, mutations and much more. Add the ability to field vehicles and customize them, and you're in for one hell of an apocalypse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Join us, as the original Toxic Holocaust miniatures game returns, from CPOP.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We welcome you to the Goremageddon. May you live, die and thrash.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goremageddon is heavily inspired by over-the-top violence, exploitation, gore, horror, humor and post apocalyptic films on the 1980s, as well as RetroWave and Thrash Metal music. Goremageddon is also CPOP's flagship project, made popular by a cult following.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
